1. Introduction
Welcome to Magic Music. We respect your privacy and want to protect your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, store, use, and disclose your personal information when you use our mobile application.
4. Sharing and Disclosure
We don’t share your personal information with third parties unless:
4.1. With Your Consent:
We might share your personal data with third parties if you explicitly give us permission to do so.
4.2. For Legal Reasons:
We might share your data if required by law or if we believe it’s necessary to comply with legal obligations.
7. Contact Us
For any questions about this privacy policy or your data, please contact us at: hello@magicmusic.pro
2. Information We Collect
2.1. Personal Information:
This includes your name, email address, phone number, and any other information you provide during registration or in your profile.
2.2. Usage Data:
We collect data related to your use of our app, such as which features you use and for how long.
2.3. Device Information:
Information about your mobile device like the device type, operating system, and other device identifiers.
5. Data Security
We implement security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
3. How We Use Your Information
3.1. To Provide Our Service:
We use your information to register your account, provide our services, and respond to your inquiries.
3.2. For Marketing:
With your consent, we might send you promotional messages and content.
3.3. To Improve Our App:
We use the data we collect to improve our app and develop new features.
6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.
